1. *On* je izgubio *šansu* za pobedom. (He lost the chance for victory.) 
2. Oni su imali *šansu* da pobede. (They had a chance to win.)
3. Oni su propustili *šansu* da se izbori za pobedu. (They missed the opportunity to fight for victory.)
4. On je dobio *šansu* da pobedi. (He got a chance to win.)
5. Ona je uzela *šansu* i probala svoje sreće. (She took a chance and tried her luck.)
6. Oni su imali *šansu* da pobede. (They had a chance to win.)